The besieged students chanted slogans which appeal for
reunification and demanded the authorities guarantee the right of
holding peaceful pro-reunification rallies and abolish the
National Security Law, which bars the pro-DPRK activities.
</P>
<P>
Though the plan of the South Korean collegians was frustrated,
a rally on reunification was held at the north side of the truce
village and some South Koreans managed to attend it, media reports
said here. 
