<P>
Former Falun Gong official Wang Liyun from Hengyang City in
central China's Hunan Province also told of the miseries he and
his wife had suffered through practicing Falun Gong.
</P>
<P>
Wang said that in 1994 he began to practise Falun Gong, in the
hope of curing his illness. His wife soon followed suit.
</P>
<P>
After two years of practicing, his wife felt an acute pain in
her abdomen, but she refused to take medicine because Li Hongzhi
had said that Falun Gong could cure any illness. She insisted on
practicing Falun Gong until January 1, 1998, when she could not
practice any more because of the pain. She was rushed to hospital,
and died of cancer in the same month.
</P>
<P>
Wang's own illness also deteriorated, but his wife's death
brought him to his senses and he went to see a doctor. Since then,
his condition has improved remarkably.
</P>
<P>
Wang said that, as a victim of Falun Gong, he is determined to
tell other people the truth about Falun Gong, from his own
experience, to reveal Li Hongzhi's evil motives.  
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
